%2520million%2Cin%2520the%2520end%2520Netflix%2520prevailed.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecrackdown%20on%20passwords%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20growth%20in%20advertising-based%20subscriptions%20contributed%20to%20Netflix's%20success%20this%20quarter.%20Company%20executives%20and%20industry%20experts%20say%20growth%20in%20Asia%20had%20a%20role%20to%20play%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou've%20got%20Japan.%20You've%20got%20Korea.%20You've%20got%20Thailand.%20You've%20got%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20Gregory%20Peters%2C%20the%20co-CEO%20of%20Netflix%2C%20said%20in%20the%20earnings%20call.%20%26quot%3BThis%20represents%2C%20again%2C%20that%20decade-plus%20investment%20in%20those%20creative%20communities%2C%20working%20with%20local%20storytellers%20there%20and%20making%20sure%20that%20they%20have%20the%20capability%20to%20tell%20their%20stories%20in%20a%20compelling%20way.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20shareholder%20letter%20on%20Thursday%2C%20Netflix%20wrote%20that%20Asia%20Pacific%20had%20the%20largest%20revenue%20growth%20rate%20of%20all%20regions%2C%20at%2019%25%2C%20compared%20to%20the%20same%20period%20last%20year.%20Revenue%20growth%20in%20North%20America%20and%20Europe%2C%20Middle%20East%2C%20and%20Africa%20was%20tied%20at%2016%25%20each.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222fa86f36-dc86-4e43-b871-a1699220d7a2%5C%22%3E'Persistence%20in%20Asia'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20industry%20experts%20who%20reacted%20to%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetflix-questions-from-wall-street-growth-ads-future-earnings-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENetflix's%20earnings%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0also%20pointed%20to%20its%20local%20content%20creation%20strategy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20of%20the%20main%20things%20about%20Netflix%20is%20just%20what%20they%20have%20done%20internationally%2C%26quot%3B%20Ben%20Silverman%2C%20the%20chairman%20and%20co-CEO%20of%20Propagate%20Content%2C%20said%20in%20a%20CNBC%20interview%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20just%20re-expressing%20content%20from%20the%20US%2C%20Netflix%20has%20also%20commissioned%20content%20in%20local%20languages%20for%20local%20markets%2C%20Silverman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENetflix's%20greatest%20success%20story%20in%20the%20region%20has%20been%20the%20South%20Korean%20production%20%26quot%3BSquid%20Game.%26quot%3B%20The%20first%20season%20of%20the%20game%20show-style%20drama%2C%20which%20was%20released%20in%202021%20and%20follows%20a%20group%20of%20debt-riddled%20contestants%20competing%20in%20deadly%20games%20for%20cash%2C%20has%20been%20watched%20265%20million%20times%20globally%20to%20date.%20It's%20also%20amassed%202.2%20billion%20hours%20of%20watch%20time%2C%20making%20it%20the%20streamer's%20most-watched%20show%20of%20all%20time%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.netflix.com%2Ftudum%2Ftop10%2Fmost-popular%2Ftv-non-english%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20Netflix%20data%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20%26quot%3BSquid%20Game%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Korean%20drama%20%26quot%3BAll%20of%20Us%20Are%20Dead%26quot%3B%20is%20also%20on%20the%20list%20of%20Netflix's%2010%20most-watched%20non-English%20language%20shows.%20The%20rest%20of%20the%20shows%20on%20the%20list%20are%20European%20and%20Mexican%20productions%2C%20three%20of%20which%20are%20different%20seasons%20of%20the%20Spanish%20hit%20%26quot%3BMoney%20Heist.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20the%20Japanese%20manga%20series%20%26quot%3BDan%20Da%20Dan%26quot%3B%20charted%20among%20the%2010%20most-watched%20shows%20in%20the%20US%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.netflix.com%2Ftudum%2Ftop10%2Funited-states%2Ftv%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENetflix%20data%20shows%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20variety%20of%20original%20content%20available%20of%20Netflix%2C%20and%20early%20investments%20in%20Japan%20and%20Korea%2C%20are%20playing%20a%20role%20in%20its%20growth%2C%20Dhivya%20T%2C%20the%20lead%20analyst%20of%20content%20and%20platform%20insights%20at%20Media%20Partners%20Asia%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNetflix's%20edge%20may%20be%20in%20its%20consistency%20and%20persistence%20in%20Asia%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20analyst%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENetflix%20appears%20committed%20to%20experimenting%20with%20different%20approaches%20to%20local%20content%20to%20meet%20local%20market%20needs%2C%20whether%20it's%20high-budget%20originals%2C%20licensing%20free%20TV%20dramas%2C%20or%20post-theatrical%20movies%2C%20the%20analyst%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBeyond%20content%2C%20lower%20pricing%20and%20a%20concerted%20crackdown%20on%20password%20sharing%20has%20also%20helped%20boost%20Netflix's%20sub%20growth%20in%20Asia's%20emerging%20markets%20over%20the%20past%20year%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENetflix%20rose%205%25%20in%20after-hours%20trading%20on%20Thursday.%20The%20company's%20stock%20is%20up%2046%25%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetflix-asia-strategy-blockbuster-q3-market-growth-2024-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729255162000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F667446932efa138e03312329%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetflix-asia-strategy-blockbuster-q3-market-growth-2024-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Netflix%20said%20Asia%20Pacific%20had%20the%20largest%20revenue%20growth%20rate%20of%20all%20regions%2C%20at%2019%25%2C%20compared%20to%20the%20same%20period%20last%20year.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22shubhangigoel%40insider.com%20(Shubhangi%20Goel)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A24%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetflix-asia-strategy-blockbuster-q3-market-growth-2024-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%221st%20Test%3A%20Virat%2C%20Sarfaraz%20score%20fifties%20as%20India%20fight%20back%20vs%20NZ%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729255043000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-114352510%2Cimgsize-55930.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fnew-zealand-in-india%2F1st-test-rohit-sharma-virat-kohli-sarfaraz-khan-score-fifties-as-india-fight-back-vs-new-zealand-on-day-3%2Farticleshow%2F114352493.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India's%20second%20innings%20in%20the%20first%20Test%20against%20New%20Zealand%20saw%20half-centuries%20from%20Virat%20Kohli%2C%20Rohit%20Sharma%2C%20and%20Sarfaraz%20Khan%2C%20ending%20the%20day%20at%20231%20for%20three.%20Kohli's%20dismissal%20off%20the%20last%20ball%20left%20India%20trailing%20by%20125%20runs.%20New%20Zealand's%20Rachin%20Ravindra%20scored%20his%20second%20Test%20century%2C%20contributing%20to%20their%20first%20innings%20total%20of%20402.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20SPORTS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fnew-zealand-in-india%2F1st-test-rohit-sharma-virat-kohli-sarfaraz-khan-score-fifties-as-india-fight-back-vs-new-zealand-on-day-3%2Farticleshow%2F114352493.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Uddhav%20Thackeray's%20Sena%20Won't%20Discuss%20Seat-Sharing%20With%20Congress's%20Nana%20Patole%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20sign%20of%20differences%20between%20the%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20faction%20of%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20and%20the%20Congress%20just%20a%20month%20before%20the%20Maharashtra%20Assembly%20elections%2C%20the%20regional%20party%20has%20said%20it%20will%20not%20hold%20seat-sharing%20discussions%20with%20state%20Congress%20President%20Nana%20Patole.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20sources%20in%20the%20opposition%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20alliance%2C%20comprising%20the%20Congress%2C%20the%20Uddhav%20Thackeray-led%20Shiv%20Sena%20and%20the%20Sharad%20Pawar%20faction%20of%20the%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20(NCP)%2C%20had%20said%20that%20a%20consensus%20had%20been%20reached%20on%20260%20of%20the%20state's%20288%20Assembly%20constituencies.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20on%20Friday%2C%20however%2C%20senior%20Shiv%20Sena%20(Uddhav%20Balasaheb%20Thackeray)%20leader%20and%20MP%20Sanjay%20Raut%20said%20the%20allies%20had%20agreed%20on%20only%20200%20seats%20and%20took%20a%20dig%20at%20Nana%20Patole%20without%20naming%20him%2C%20saying%20leaders%20in%20the%20Maharashtra%20Congress%20leaders%20are%20%26quot%3Bnot%20capable%20of%20taking%20decisions%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Raut%20said%20he%20had%20spoken%20to%20Congress%20general%20secretaries%20KC%20Venugopal%20and%20Mukul%20Wasnik%20and%20the%20party's%20Maharashtra%20in-charge%20Ramesh%20Chennithala%20and%20would%20also%20talk%20to%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20later%20in%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20pending%20decision%20should%20be%20expedited.%20Very%20little%20time%20is%20left.%20Maharashtra%20Congress%20leaders%20are%20not%20capable%20of%20making%20decisions.%20They%20have%20to%20send%20the%20list%20to%20Delhi%20frequently%20and%20then%20discussions%20happen.%20The%20decision%20(on%20seat-sharing)%20will%20have%20to%20be%20taken%20at%20the%20earliest%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20news%20agency%20ANI.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20told%20NDTV%20that%20the%20differences%20between%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20and%20the%20Congress%20arose%20because%20the%20Uddhav%20Thackeray-led%20party%20wanted%20to%20contest%20more%20seats%20in%20the%20Vidarbha%20region%2C%20which%20Mr%20Patole%20was%20not%20willing%20to%20concede.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERiding%20high%20on%20its%20performance%20in%20Maharashtra%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20in%20which%20it%20emerged%20as%20the%20single-largest%20party%20with%2013%20of%2048%20seats%2C%20the%20Congress%20is%20hoping%20to%20do%20well%20in%20Vidarbha%2C%20where%20it%20has%20had%20a%20good%20track%20record%20in%20previous%20elections%20as%20well.%20The%20region%20is%20also%20a%20stronghold%20of%20Mr%20Patole.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20Mr%20Chennithala%20will%20meet%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20at%20his%20residence%20in%20Mumbai%20to%20sort%20out%20the%20differences%20between%20the%20parties.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20it%20is%20unclear%20what%20impact%20the%20decision%20of%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20will%20have%20on%20the%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%2C%20sources%20said%20the%20differences%20may%20hurt%20the%20coalition%20in%20its%20fight%20with%20the%20ruling%20Mahayuti%20alliance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%20alliance%20was%20seen%20to%20be%20in%20the%20driver's%20seat%20after%20its%20performance%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20in%20which%20it%20managed%20to%20win%2030%20constituencies%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20but%20the%20BJP-Shiv%20Sena%20(Eknath%20Shinde%20faction)-NCP%20(Ajit%20Pawar)%20faction%20coalition%20has%20been%20energised%20after%20the%20Haryana%20results%20in%20which%20the%20BJP%20managed%20to%20pull%20off%20its%20best-ever%20performance%20despite%20battling%20anti-incumbency%20after%20two%20straight%20terms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVoting%20in%20Maharashtra%20will%20be%20held%20in%20a%20single%20phase%20on%20November%2020%20and%20counting%20will%20take%20place%20on%20November%2023.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729254960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fqm7vralo_maha-vikas-aghadi-leaders_625x300_17_October_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fuddhav-thackerays-shiv-sena-faction-wont-discuss-maharashtra-seat-sharing-with-state-congress-chief-nana-patole-sources-6818239%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20sign%20of%20differences%20between%20the%20Uddhav%20Thackeray-led%20Shiv%20Sena%20and%20the%20Congress%20just%20a%20month%20before%20the%20Maharashtra%20Assembly%20polls%2C%20the%20regi