f%20visceral%20threat%20of%20annihilation%20that%20hangs%20over%20the%20whole%20piece.%20I%20think%20you%20get%20older%20and%20you%20experience%20difficult%20things%20in%20your%20life%20and%20that%20just%20doesn't%20feel%20like%20unfamiliar%20territory%20anymore.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20Kendrick%20is%20self-aware%20enough%20to%20know%20people%20may%20be%20surprised%20that%20her%20latest%20project%20is%20a%20far%20cry%20from%20a%20cappella%20group%20hijinks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20though%20this%20is%20a%20pretty%20extreme%20genre%20in%20comparison%20to%20what%20I'm%20known%20for%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20felt%20very%20personally%20attached%20to%20the%20material.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20latest%20interview%20in%20Business%20Insider's%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Frole-play-series%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%26quot%3BRole%20Play%26quot%3B%20series%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Kendrick%20reminisces%20about%20being%20a%20fly%20on%20the%20wall%20while%20filming%20the%20%26quot%3BTwilight%26quot%3B%20franchise%2C%20addresses%20those%20%26quot%3BPitch%20Perfect%204%26quot%3B%20rumors%2C%20and%20teases%20the%20twisty%20sequel%20to%20%26quot%3BA%20Simple%20Favor.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222623590d-7ee7-430c-b507-289b7bef49c7%5C%22%3EOn%20being%20a%20'bystander'%20to%20the%20'Twilight'%20pop%20culture%20phenomenon%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Anna%20Kendrick%20as%20Jessica%20Stanley%20in%20%26quot%3BThe%20Twilight%20Saga%3A%20Breaking%20Dawn%20%E2%80%94%20Part%201.%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66f6c2f1f9f6733e4be03d7d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAnna%20Kendrick%20as%20Jessica%20Stanley%20in%20%26quot%3BThe%20Twilight%20Saga%3A%20Breaking%20Dawn%20%E2%80%94%20Part%201.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3ESummit%20Entertainment%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIt's%20been%2016%20years%20since%20the%20first%20%26quot%3BTwilight%26quot%3B%20movie%20came%20out.%20Is%20there%20anything%20that%20you%20look%20back%20on%20now%20and%20view%20differently%20about%20the%20franchise%20and%20the%20time%20you%20spent%20on%20it%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20guess%20I%20don't%20really%20view%20it%20that%20differently%20because%20my%20experience%20was%20really%20unique%20in%20that%20cast.%20Almost%20everyone%20else%20in%20the%20cast%20had%20to%20treat%20every%20moment%20like%20life%20and%20death%2C%20good%20versus%20evil%2C%20our%20eternal%20souls%20are%20on%20the%20line%20%E2%80%94%20and%20all%20I%20had%20to%20do%20was%20show%20up%20and%20make%20a%20snarky%20comment%20as%20I%20kind%20of%20pass%20through%20the%20frame.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20I%20really%20felt%20like%20such%20a%20bystander%20to%20it%20in%20a%20way%20that%20I%20was%20very%20grateful%20to%20be%20privy%20to%20this%20kind%20of%20cultural%20phenomenon%20without%20it%20really%20impacting%20me%20in%20the%20ways%20that%20I%20think%20would've%20felt%20really%20challenging%20and%20overwhelming.%20The%20fans%20of%20those%20books%20are%20so%20invested%20that%20even%20if%20you%20came%20into%20the%20franchise%20really%20late%20and%20you%20had%20one%20line%2C%20but%20you%20were%20playing%20a%20vampire%20or%20a%20werewolf%2C%20they're%20obsessed%20with%20you.%20They're%20picking%20apart%20every%20detail%20of%20your%20costume%20and%20your%20gestures%20and%20whatever%2C%20and%20I%20just%20didn't%20have%20that%20level%20of%20responsibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20could%20imagine%20people%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BOh%2C%20I%20wish%20I%20could%20have%20been%20a%20fly%20on%20the%20wall%20to%20the%20whole%20'Twilight'%20set%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20I%20am%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BOh%2C%20I%20kind%20of%20got%20to%20be%20that.%26quot%3B%20I%20just%20really%20wasn't%20in%20the%20thick%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226186460f-27d5-4c93-8e2d-9f9150516f01%5C%22%3EOn%20her%20'Up%20in%20the%20Air'%20costar%20George%20Clooney's%20small%20acts%20of%20kindness%20and%20those%20'Pitch%20Perfect%204'%20rumors%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222146%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rebel%20Wilson%20as%20Amy%20and%20Anna%20Kendrick%20as%20Beca%20in%20%26quot%3BPitch%20Perfect%203.%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F660e7bb91caec1275a6cb921%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221422%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERebel%20Wilson%20as%20Amy%20and%20Anna%20Kendrick%20as%20Beca%20in%20%26quot%3BPitch%20Perfect%203.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EUniversal%20Pictures%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGeorge%20Clooney%20has%20a%20reputation%20for%20being%20a%20classy%20guy%20in%20Hollywood.%20What%20did%20you%20learn%20from%20working%20with%20someone%20of%20that%20caliber%20early%20in%20your%20career%20on%20%26quot%3BUp%20in%20the%20Air%3F%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGeorge%20is%20so%20generous%20in%20every%20way%20as%20an%20actor.%20He%20was%20really%20the%20first%20person%20that%20I%20worked%20with%20where%20I%20would%20see%20him%20listening%20to%20the%20notes%20that%20other%20actors%20would%20get%2C%20and%20he%20would%20adjust%20his%20off-camera%20performance%20to%20help%20elicit%20whatever%20adjustment%20was%20called%20for.%20And%20I%20think%20that%20that's%20just%20the%20sign%20of%20somebody%20really%20willing%20to%20extend%20themselves%20for%20someone%20else.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20first%20day%2C%20the%20first%20shot%20that%20I%20was%20in%20on%20my%20first%20day%20of%20filming%2C%20he%20said%20something%20to%20me%20kind%20of%20under%20his%20breath%20almost%20about%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BMan%2C%20do%20you%20get%20nervous%20on%20the%20first%20day%3F%20I%20get%20so%20nervous.%26quot%3B%20And%20at%20the%20time%2C%20I%20was%20just%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BYeah%2C%20totally.%20I%20get%20really%20nervous.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20wasn't%20until%20eight%20years%20later%20or%20something%20that%20it%20occurred%20to%20me%20that%20he%20does%20not%20get%20nervous%2C%20but%20that%20was%20so%20sweet%20of%20him%20to%20say.%20For%20him%20to%20not%20just%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BHey%2C%20it's%20OK%20if%20you're%20nervous%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20to%20take%20it%20on%20himself%20as%20though%2C%20%26quot%3BHey%2C%20kid%2C%20we're%20in%20this%20together%2C%26quot%3B%20was%20just%20the%20sweetest%20thing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20have%20to%20ask%20about%20%26quot%3BPitch%20Perfect.%26quot%3B%20In%20April%2C%20Rebel%20Wilson%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.radiotimes.com%2Fmovies%2Frebel-wilson-pitch-perfect-4-development-newsupdate%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3Esaid%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%20a%20fourth%20movie%20was%20possibly%20in%20development%2C%20and%20then%20Anna%20Camp%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscreenrant.com%2Fpitch-perfect-4-movie-update-anna-camp-aubrey-story%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3Esaid%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%20she%20didn't%20think%20so.%20Then%20Elizabeth%20Banks%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.yahoo.com%2Fentertainment%2Felizabeth-banks-reveals-pitch-perfect-185743449.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3Esaid%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%2C%20%26quot%3BThey're%20always%20talking%20about%20it.%26quot%3B%20So%20please%20tell%20me%3A%20what%20is%20going%20on%3F%20Do%20you%20have%20any%20updates%20on%20your%20end%20about%20a%20fourth%20movie%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWell%2C%20I%20have%20no%20earthly%20idea.%20Frankly%2C%20I'm%20hearing%20some%20of%20this%20from%20you.%20I'll%20say%20that%20sometimes%20on%20the%20group%20chat%20that%20we%20all%20have%2C%20we%20sort%20of%20lament%20that%20everyone%20is%20so%20busy%20and%20working%20all%20the%20time%2C%20which%20is%20wonderful%2C%20of%20course.%20But%20it%20means%20that%20we're%20almost%20never%20able%20to%20get%20all%20of%20us%20in%20a%20room%20at%20the%20same%20time%20whenever%20we%20try%20to%20find%20a%20date%20that%20would%20work%20for%20everybody.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20it%20does%20sort%20of%20feel%20like%2C%20oh%20God%2C%20would%20it%20take%20another%20movie%20to%20ensure%20that%20we%20were%20all%20actually%20in%20the%20same%20place%20at%20the%20same%20time%20again%3F%20So%20I%20don't%20know.%20I%20guess%20selfishly%2C%20that's%20almost%20the%20main%20reason%20that%20I%20would%20wish%20for%20such%20a%20thing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOne%20of%20your%20other%20big%20movies%20is%20%26quot%3BInto%20the%20Woods.%26quot%3B%20What%20did%20you%20learn%20or%20observe%20from%20working%20alongside%20people%20like%20Meryl%20Streep%20and%20Chris%20Pine%3F%20That's%20a%20mega%20cast%20in%20general.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20always%20hard%20to%20put%20into%20words%20what%20you%20learn%20from%20working%20with%20people%20because%20they're%20not%20sitting%20you%20down%20and%20having%20a%20talk%20with%20you.%20But%20I'll%20say%20that%20Meryl%20very%20much%20has%20that%20Clooney%20thing%20of%20being%20exactly%20what%20you%20want%20them%20to%20be%2C%20exactly%20what%20you'd%20hope%20for%2C%20and%20being%20really%2C%20really%20generous.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20anything%2C%20I%20think%20it%20was%20interesting%20to%20see%20people%20who%20were%20so%20established%20and%20so%20talented%20and%20had%20so%20much%20experience%20watching%20how%20almost%20every%20single%20person%20was%20feeling%20insecure%20about%20singing.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20very%20sweet.%20It%20really%20was%20this%20level%20playing%20field%20because%20Sondheim's%20music%20is%20so%20difficult%20that%20it%20really%20felt%20like%20any%20hierarchy%20that%20might%20have%20formed%20just%20never%20had%20a%20chance%20to%20take%20hold%20because%20everybody%20was%20kind%20of%20equally%20terrified%20about%20singing%20the%20songs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C