-8d3f-11ef-9f97-6f2e4c64dcd9.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcly24q16ev0o%231%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Three%20Americans%20were%20arrested%2C%20with%20Venezuela%20accusing%20them%20of%20working%20with%20US%20spy%20agencies.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A29%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcly24q16ev0o%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcly24q16ev0o.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcly24q16ev0o.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Former%20Delhi%20Health%20Minister%20Satyendar%20Jain%20Gets%20Bail%20After%202%20Years%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFormer%20Delhi%20minister%20and%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20leader%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fsearch%3Fsearchtext%3Dsatyendar-jain%5C%22%3ESatyendar%20Jain%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20been%20granted%20bail%20by%20a%20local%20court%20in%20a%20money%20laundering%20case.%20Mr%20Jain%20was%20arrested%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20over%20two%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20granted%20him%20interim%20bail%20in%20May%202023%20on%20medical%20grounds.%20He%20returned%20to%20Delhi's%20Tihar%20jail%20after%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20denied%20his%20request%20for%20regular%20bail%20in%20March%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BConsidering%20the%20delay%20in%20trial%20and%20long%20incarceration%20of%2018%20months%2C%20and%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20trail%20will%20take%20a%20long%20time%20to%20start%2C%20let%20alone%20conclude%2C%20the%20accused%20is%20favourably%20suited%20for%20the%20relief%2C%26quot%3B%20special%20judge%20Vishal%20Gogne%20said%2C%20according%20to%20news%20agency%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Jain%20is%20the%20third%20AAP%20leader%20who%20has%20been%20granted%20bail%20in%20different%20cases%20in%20recent%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E