than%20ever%2C%20people%20are%20stepping%20up%2C%20contributing%20larger%20sums%2C%20and%20actively%20engaging%20in%20the%20political%20process.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%24145%2C000%20median%20income%20of%20Indian%20American%20households%20is%2021%25%20higher%20than%20the%20overall%20US%20median.%20Shekar%20Narasimhan%2C%20founder%20and%20chairman%20of%20the%20AAPI%20Victory%20Fund%2C%20the%20largest%20Super%20PAC%20(political%20action%20committee)%20in%20the%20Asian%20American%20diaspora%2C%20says%20that%20even%20though%20it%20is%20not%20easy%20to%20find%20accurate%20data%20on%20how%20much%20finance%20Indian%20Americans%20are%20pumping%20into%20campaigns%2C%20there%20are%20huge%20donors%20in%20the%20community.%20This%20is%20evident%20from%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20Democratic%20National%20Finance%20Committee%20is%205%25%20Indian-American%20even%20as%20their%20share%20in%20the%20US%20population%20is%20only%201%25.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20small-dollar%20donors%20are%20important%20too%2C%20adds%20Narasimhan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EM.R.%20Rangaswami%2C%20Indiaspora's%20Founder%20%26amp%3B%20Chairman%2C%20also%20notes%20the%20remarkable%20volume%20of%20funds%20being%20generated.%20%26quot%3BNow%20we%20have%20two%20healthy%20PACs%20with%20the%20AAPI%20Victory%20Fund%20and%20the%20Indian%20American%20Impact%20Fund%2C%20so%20more%20and%20more%20money%20is%20coming%20in%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%20The%20Indian%20American%20Impact%2C%20the%20largest%20desi%20PAC%2C%20is%20also%20identifying%20and%20training%20the%20next%20batch%20of%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Sangay%20Mishra%2C%20associate%20professor%20of%20Political%20Science%20at%20Drew%20University%20and%20author%20of%20%3Cem%3EDesis%20Divided%3A%20The%20Political%20Lives%20of%20South%20Asian%20Americans%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20found%20in%20his%20research%20that%20since%202012%2C%20Indian%20Americans%20have%20been%20%26quot%3Bvery%20visible%26quot%3B%20in%20%26quot%3Bbundling%26quot%3B%20contributions%20for%20campaigns.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20seen%20that%20kind%20of%20outsized%20influence%20because%20of%20the%20number%20of%20very%20wealthy%20fundraisers%20organised%20in%20the%20community%20networks%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20popular%20saying%20that%20the%20road%20to%20the%20White%20House%20goes%20through%20Silicon%20Valley%20-%20the%20hub%20of%20affluent%20Indians%20in%20tech.%20Harris's%20recent%20California%20fundraisers%20generated%20%2455%20million%20over%20a%20weekend%3B%20she%20has%20raised%20a%20billion%20dollars%20since%20becoming%20the%20nominee.%20Powerful%20fundraisers%2C%20including%20the%20one%20hosted%20by%20the%20billionaire%20AI%20investor%20and%20technologist%20Vinod%20Khosla%20for%20the%20Democratic%20campaign%20this%20election%20cycle%2C%20made%20news%20waves.%20There%20are%20more%20than%2060%20Indian%20names%20on%20the%20list%20of%20VCs%20for%20Kamala.%20Other%20business%20leaders%20and%20founders%20endorsing%20her%20include%20corporate%20leaders%20like%20Indra%20Nooyi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Enduring%20Republican%20Vote%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Harris's%20candidacy%20has%20further%20loosened%20the%20purse%20strings%20of%20enthused%20Democrats%2C%20Donald%20Trump's%20Indian%20American%20supporters%2C%20including%20Vivek%20Ramaswamy%2C%20have%20stayed%20loyal%20to%20the%20Republican%20Party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESampat%20Shivangi%2C%20an%20old-time%20Republican%20faithful%20and%20the%20only%20Indian%20American%20delegate%20at%20the%20Republican%20National%20Convention%20this%20year%2C%20has%20been%20elected%20to%20the%20body%20for%20the%20sixth%20time.%20He%20is%20sending%20a%20big%20cheque%20for%20Trump's%20campaign.%20Then%20there%20is%20hotelier%20Danny%20Gaekwad%2C%20who%20has%20contributed%20to%20the%20campaigns%20of%20every%20Republican%20Presidential%20candidate%20since%20George%20Bush.%20%26quot%3BThe%20October%20event%20involved%20an%20insane%20amount%20of%20money.%20People%20known%20to%20me%20are%20calling%20me%20-%20Bhau%2C%20I%20want%20to%20go%2C%20my%20wife%20wants%20to%20go%2C%26quot%3B%20Gaekwad%20says%20about%20a%20sold-out%20fundraiser.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERepublicans%20like%20Shivangi%20say%20they%20support%20Trump%20because%20%26quot%3BHarris%20is%20not%20a%20friend%20of%20India%26quot%3B.%20Along%20with%20accusations%20of%20%26quot%3Bdiluting%26quot%3B%20her%20Indian%20American%20identity%2C%20they%20point%20out%20that%20she%20failed%20to%20visit%20India%20during%20her%20years%20as%20Vice-President.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERepublicans%2C%20however%2C%20do%20acknowledge%20that%20the%20fervour%20among%20Indian%20American%20supporters%20of%20the%20party%2C%20especially%20Hindus%2C%20has%20waned%20since%202020%2C%20when%20President%20Trump%20and%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20friendly%20ties%20created%20a%20huge%20buzz.%20%26quot%3B%7BPerhaps%20because%5D%20he%20is%20a%20third-time%20candidate%2C%26quot%3B%20Gaekwad%20reasons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20wooed%20by%20both%20parties%2C%20by%20and%20large%2C%20Indian%20Americans%20have%20voted%20for%20Democrats.%20A%202024%20AAPI%20Data%20survey%20found%20that%2055%25%20of%20Indian%20Americans%20identify%20as%20Democrats%2C%2025%25%20as%20Republicans%20and%2015%25%20as%20Independents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ESway%20In%20Swing%20States%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20American%20community%20is%20critical%20for%20both%20parties%20because%20even%20though%20they%20make%20up%20only%201%25%20of%20the%20US%20population%2C%20about%20a%20third%20of%20them%20reside%20in%20Presidential%20battleground%20states%20like%20Michigan%20and%20Georgia%2C%20where%20they%20can%20play%20a%20huge%20role%20in%20shaping%20the%20results.%20Recalling%20the%20narrow%20Democratic%20victory%20in%20Georgia%20in%202020%2C%20Mishra%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BIn%20a%20state%20like%20that%2C%20it%20matters%20because%20the%20margin%20was%20so%20thin.%20Indian%20Americans%20voted%20one%20way%20and%20the%20election%20went%20that%20way%2C%20if%20they%20had%20voted%20the%20other%20way%20results%20might%20have%20been%20different.%26quot%3B%20The%20last%20few%20Presidential%20elections%20have%20been%20close%20calls%2C%20decided%20by%20narrow%20gaps%20in%20a%20handful%20of%20states.%20Polls%20show%20that%20the%20current%20one%20seems%20evenly%20poised.%20There%20are%20nearly%204%2C00%2C000%20voters%20of%20South%20Asian%20descent%20in%20the%2010%20most%20contested%20swing%20states.%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20sizeable%20number%20of%20Indian%20Americans%20who%20can%20make%20a%20difference%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Dr%20Mishra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThus%2C%20volunteers%20of%20the%20highly%20politically%20engaged%20community%20utilise%20their%20resources%20strategically%20in%20pivotal%20states.%20Based%20in%20the%20Democratic%20stronghold%20California%2C%20Sangeeta%20Ramakrishnan%20is%20They%20See%20Blue's%20'lead'%20for%20swing%20state%20calls.%20She%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BThere%20are%20more%20of%20us%20in%20blue%20states%20and%20because%20you%20don't%20need%20to%20knock%20those%20many%20doors%20here%2C%20it's%20better%20to%20use%20our%20resources%20effectively.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20election%2C%20Pennsylvania's%20Buck's%20County%20gains%20the%20reputation%20of%20being%20the%20%26quot%3Bswingiest%20county%20in%20the%20swingiest%20state%26quot%3B.%20Rupa%20Mohan%2C%20a%20volunteer%20at%20They%20See%20Blue%2C%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20phone%20banks%20run%20by%20Gujarati%20volunteers%2C%20Malayalam%20speakers%2C%20Urdu%20speakers.%20We%20have%20a%20whole%20pile%20of%20different%20volunteers%20lined%20up.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOverall%20as%20well%2C%20the%20political%20participation%20of%20the%204.8%20million-strong%20young%20immigrant%20community%20is%20soaring.%20In%20the%20last%20two%20presidential%20elections%2C%20they%20had%20the%20highest%20voter%20turnout%20among%20Asian%20Americans%2C%20on%20par%20with%20white%20voter%20turnout.%20As%20many%20as%2071%25%20of%20eligible%20Indian%20Americans%20voted%20in%202020%2C%20a%209-point%20increase%20from%202016.%20This%20trend%20is%20expected%20to%20continue.%20A%20recent%20Asian%20American%20voter%20survey%20shows%20that%20around%2091%25%20of%20Indian%20Americans%20plan%20to%20vote%20in%20this%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EOffice%20Dreams%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20only%20electoral%20numbers%20that%20elevate%20the%20Indian%20Americans'%20political%20profile%20-%20they%20also%20nurture%20strong%20ambitions%20for%20office.%20From%20the%20highest%20level%20-%20the%20Presidential%20post%20-%20to%20Congress%2C%20state%20senates%2C%20assemblies%2C%20district%20attorneys%2C%20city%20councils%2C%20to%20school%20boards%2C%20their%20numbers%20are%20huge.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20one%20really%20has%20a%20count%20of%20how%20many%20Indian%20American%20candidates%20are%20in%20the%202024%20race.%20But%20there%20are%20five%20Indian%20Americans%20in%20the%20current%20US%20Congress%2C%20and%2C%20after%20the%20coming%20election%2C%20says%20Narasimhan%2C%20the%20community%20will%20likely%20have%20seven.%20Getting%20to%20that%20number%20took%20decades%20since%20the%20first%20Indian%20American%20was%20voted%20to%20the%20Congress%20in%201956.%20But%20the%20rise%20in%20the%20last%2020%20years%20has%20been%20exponential%2C%20thanks%20to%20second-generation%20Indian%20Americans%20and%20their%20education%20levels%2C%20which%20are%20far%20higher%20than%20the%20US%20average.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20their%20numbers%20in%20administration%2C%20while%20Indian%20Americans%20constitute%20just%200.6%25%20of%20the%20adult%20citizen%20population%20in%20the%20US%2C%20they%20hold%20about%204.4%25%20of%20senior%20positions%20in%20government.%20There%20are%20over%20150%20Indian%20Americans%20in%20the%20Biden-Harris%20administration%2C%20and%20that%20is%20projected%20to%20increase%20by%20over%2050%20if%20Harris%20becomes%20President.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Pursuit%20Of%20Influence%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20conquered%20every%20metric%20on%20the%20ladder%20of%20ascent%20-%20votes%2C%20money%20and%20candidates%20-%20Indian%20American%20leaders%20are%20aspiring%20for%20political%20representation%20similar%20to%20what%20the%20much%20older%20Jewish%20American%20population%20enjoys.%20Jews%20constitute%20about%202%25%20of%20the%20American%20population%20but%20make%20up%2010%25%20of%20the%20US%20Congress.%20%26quot%3BIn%20force%2C%20we%20have%20been%20here%20for%20about%2030%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Rangaswami.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%207%25%20of%20US%20physicians%2C%2010%25%20of%20the%20American%20IT%20sector%20and%20are%20well-represented%20in%20academia%20and%20government%2C%20so%20why%20not%20have%20clout.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlready%2C%20with%20early%20voting%20having%20begun%2C%20supporters%20of%20both%20parties%20are%20canvassing%20aggressively%20through%20door-to-door%20promotions%2C%20postcards%2C%20phone%20calls%2C%20and%20texts.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20going%20to%20heat%20up%20in%20the%20next%20few%20weeks!%26quot%3B%20says%20Shobha%20Chokkalingam%2C%20Atlanta-based%20leader%20of%20the%20Georgia%20chapter%20of%20the%20American%20Hindu%20Coalition.%20But%20it's%20'desi'%20Democratic%20supporters%20for%20whom%20this%20election%20is%20particularly%20special.%20With%20Kamala%20Harris%20in%20the%20race%2C%20the%20Indian%20American%20community%20is%20eager%20to%20play%20a%20part%20in%20making%20history.%20Rangaswami%20sums%20it%20up%20well%3A%20%26quot%3BIf%20Kamala%20Harris%20becomes%20president%20-%20I%20mean%20keep%20in%20mind%20there's%20been%20no%20Jewish%20president%20in%20the%20US%20-%20this%20could%20be%20a%20huge%20thing.%20So%20let's%20see!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Savita%20Patel%20is%20a%20San%20Francisco%20Bay%20Area-based%20journalist%20and%20producer.%20She%20reports%20on%20the%20Indian%20diaspora%2C%20India-US%20ties%