%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20pungent%20foam%20contains%20high%20levels%20of%20ammonia%20and%20phosphates%2C%20posing%20serious%20health%20risks%2C%20including%20respiratory%20and%20skin%20problems%2C%20environmental%20experts%20told%20news%20agency%20PTI.%20They%20said%20the%20pollution%20levels%20in%20the%20river%20are%20alarming%20and%20urged%20the%20government%20to%20tackle%20it%20on%20a%20war%20footing%20because%20major%20festivals%20like%20Chhath%20Puja%20are%20approaching.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20kind%20of%20foam%20formation%20is%20common%20when%20fats%20from%20decaying%20plants%20and%20pollutants%20mix%20with%20the%20water%2C%20but%20its%20presence%20during%20the%20monsoon%20is%20surprising%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20expert%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20the%20news%20agency%2C%20attributing%20the%20frothing%20to%20the%20absence%20of%20flood%20spells%20that%20typically%20wash%20away%20pollutants.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FWATCH%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23WATCH%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%20Delhi%3A%20Toxic%20foam%20seen%20floating%20on%20the%20Yamuna%20River.%20Visuals%20from%20Kalindi%20Kunj.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FtXeBtNk4MI%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FtXeBtNk4MI%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20ANI%20(%40ANI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1847124987595182321%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EOctober%2018%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECentral%20Pollution%20Control%20Board%20(CPCB)%20data%20showed%20that%2C%20as%20of%209%20am%20on%20Friday%2C%20the%20AQI%20was%20also%20in%20the%20very%20poor%20category%20(between%20301%20and%20400)%20in%20several%20parts%20of%20Delhi.%20In%20north%20Delhi's%20Wazirpur%2C%20the%20AQI%20was%20379%20while%20in%20east%20Delhi's%20Vivek%20Vihar%2C%20it%20stood%20at%20327.%20The%20figure%20was%20337%20in%20central%20Delhi's%20Shadipur%20and%20312%20in%20west%20Delhi's%20Punjabi%20Bagh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%20Environment%20Minister%20Gopal%20Rai%20said%20different%20local%20sources%20of%20pollution%20have%20been%20identified%20at%2013%20hotspots%20in%20the%20capital%20and%2080%20anti-smog%20guns%20will%20be%20deployed%20to%20keep%20dust%20in%20check.%20Each%20of%20the%20hotspots%2C%20he%20said%2C%20will%20have%20a%20coordination%20committee%20to%20act%20against%20local%20sources%20of%20pollution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20political%20blame%20game%20also%20continued%2C%20with%20North%20East%20Delhi%20MP%20and%20BJP%20leader%20Manoj%20Tiwari%20saying%20that%20the%20AAP%20government%20in%20Delhi%20does%20not%20want%20to%20tackle%20pollution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BArvind%20Kejriwal%20was%20the%20chief%20minister%20for%2010%20years%20and%20Atishi%20has%20been%20in%20the%20post%20for%20a%20month.%20They%20have%20no%20intention%20of%20tackling%20pollution%20and%20letting%20the%20people%20of%20Delhi%20breathe.%20Pollution%20is%20turning%20fatal%20again%20-%20from%20the%20air%20to%20the%20river%20-%20and%20this%20is%20just%20the%20beginning%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHitting%20back%2C%20Mr%20Rai%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20doing%20everything%20to%20curb%20pollution.%20It%20is%20the%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20government%20that%20ensured%2024-hour%20power%20and%20reduced%20the%20smoke%20from%20generators.%20The%20BJP%20is%20a%20party%20that%20spreads%20pollution%2C%20our%20party%20reduces%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729247940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2F3f81lu6_yamuna-froth_625x300_18_October_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-pollution-yamuna-frothing-delhi-video-yamuna-blanketed-in-toxic-froth-delhi-air-quality-remains-poor-6818238%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20double%20whamm