0abuse%20content%20is%20increasingly%20being%20found%20on%20publicly%20accessible%20areas%20of%20the%20internet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.iwf.org.uk%2Fnews-media%2Fnews%2Fpublic-exposure-to-chilling-ai-child-sexual-abuse-images-and-videos-increases%2F%5C%22%3Ereport%20by%20the%20Internet%20Watch%20Foundation%3C%2Fa%3E%20(IWF)%2C%20AI-generated%20child%20sexual%20abuse%20content%20is%20exposing%20even%20more%20people%20to%20the%20harmful%20and%20horrific%20imagery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20the%20images%20and%20videos%20of%20children%20being%20hurt%20and%20abused%20are%20so%20realistic%20that%20they%20can%20be%20very%20difficult%20to%20tell%20apart%20from%20imagery%20of%20real%20children%20and%20are%20regarded%20as%20criminal%20content%20in%20the%20eyes%20of%20UK%20law%2C%20much%20in%20the%20same%20way%20as%20'traditional'%20child%20sexual%20abuse%20material%20would%20be%2C%20as%20per%20the%20IWF.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%20six%20months%20alone%2C%20analysts%20at%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.iwf.org.uk%2Fnews-media%2Fnews%2Fpublic-exposure-to-chilling-ai-child-sexual-abuse-images-and-videos-increases%2F%5C%22%3EIWF%20%3C%2Fa%3Ehave%20seen%20a%206%25%20increase%20in%20confirmed%20reports%20containing%20AI-generated%20child%20sexual%20abuse%20material%2C%20compared%20with%20the%20preceding%2012%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IWF%20is%20warning%20that%20almost%20all%20the%20content%20(99%25)%20was%20found%20on%20publicly%20available%20areas%20of%20the%20internet%20and%20was%20not%20hidden%20on%20the%20dark%20web.%20Most%20of%20the%20reports%20have%20come%20from%20members%20of%20the%20public%20(78%25)%20who%20have%20stumbled%20across%20the%20criminal%20imagery%20on%20sites%20such%20as%20forums%20or%20AI%20galleries.%20The%20remainder%20were%20actioned%20by%20IWF%20analysts%20through%20proactive%20searching.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnalysts%20say%20that%20viewing%20AI-generated%20cont