quot%3Bslaughtering%20of%20Gazans%26quot%3B%20over%20the%20past%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20in%20distress%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20sighed.%20%26quot%3BWe%20young%20Saudis%20can%20see%20Gaza%20being%20flattened%2C%20but%20my%20country%20stays%20silent.%26quot%3B%20These%20are%20brave%20words%20from%20a%20Saudi%2C%20no%20doubt%20on%20foreign%20land.%20But%20then%2C%20it's%20a%20country%20where%20the%20closest%20thing%20to%20freedom%20of%20speech%20is%20the%20freedom%20to%20agree%20with%20the%20monarch.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20what%20really%20made%20the%20conversation%20interesting%20was%20his%20view%20on%20Iran's%20missile%20strike%20against%20Israel%20on%20October%201.%20%26quot%3BIran%20is%20the%20only%20country%20standing%20up%20to%20Israel%20and%20America%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20admiration%20and%20relief.%20A%20Sunni%20Saudi%20praising%20a%20Shiite%20Iran%20is%20like%20an%20Iranian%20praising%20Israel.%20It%20should%20give%20Crown%20Prince%20Mohammed%20bin%20Salman%20a%20sleepless%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20weeks%20ago%2C%20an%20avalanche%20of%20missiles%20rained%20down%20over%20Israeli%20skies%2C%20causing%20limited%20damage%20but%20sending%20shockwaves%20through%20the%20Muslim%20world.%20From%20Jakarta%20to%20Jenin%2C%20the%20celebrations%20were%20will%20-%C2%A0%20people%20cheering%20as%20though%20it%20was%20Israel's%20final%20defeat.%20Screams%2C%20slogans%2C%20sheer%20disbelief.%20Never%20mind%20that%20Israel's%20inevitable%20retaliation%2C%20which%20is%20yet%20to%20come%2C%20could%20be%20even%20more%20spectacularly%20deadly.%20For%20them%2C%20the%20mere%20fact%20that%20someone%20-%20anyone%20-%20had%20dared%20to%20defy%20Israel%20was%20enough.%20Forget%20logic.%20This%20was%20emotional%20catharsis%20at%20its%20peak.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20not%20surprising%20then%20that%20Tehran's%20defiance%20against%20Israel%20and%20the%20US%20is%20making%20the%20Islamic%20Republic%20more%20popular%20across%20both%20the%20wider%20Shiite%20and%20Sunni%20communities.%20It%20is%20important%20to%20recall%20the%202006%20Lebanese%20war%2C%20when%20Iran's%20active%20support%20to%20Hezbollah%20against%20Israel%20generated%20a%20surge%20in%20support%20for%20Iran%20across%20the%20Muslim%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EIran's%20Soft%20Power%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Iranian%20people's%20revolution%20is%20just%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20revolution%20for%20the%20entire%20Islamic%20world.%26quot%3B%20Those%20were%20the%20words%20of%20Ayatollah%20Ruhollah%20Khomeini%2C%20the%20man%20who%20kickstarted%20the%201979%20Iranian%20Revolution%20and%20essentially%20declared%20his%20intention%20to%20export%20Iran's%20brand%20of%20Islamic%20revival%20far%20and%20wide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20policymakers%20and%20analysts%20in%20the%20West%20tend%20to%20fixate%20on%20the%20Islamic%20Revolutionary%20Guard%20Corps%20(IRGC)%20and%20its%20well-trained%20armed%20militias%2C%20they%20are%20really%20just%20scratching%20the%20surface.%20Sure%2C%20the%20IRGC's%20militia%20network%20packs%20a%20punch%2C%20but%20that's%20only%20one%20part%20of%20Iran's%20influence.%20The%20real%20thing%20happens%20behind%20the%20scenes%2C%20where%20Iran%20has%20built%20a%20whole%20soft-power%20empire%20across%20West%20Asia%20-%20and%20beyond%20-thanks%20to%20its%20soft-power%20agencies.%20Under%20Iran's%20current%20supreme%20leader%2C%20Ayatollah%20Ali%20Khamenei%2C%20Iran%20has%20continued%20with%20its%20policy%20of%20exporting%20its%20revolution.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20export%20of%20its%20ideology%20is%20enshrined%20in%20its%20Constitution%20implemented%20after%20the%201979%20revolution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20Iran%20cannot%20do%20militarily%20to%20Israel%2C%20it's%20doing%20with%20its%20soft%20power.%20It%20has%20encircled%20the%20Jewish%20state%20with%20a%20web%20of%20entities%20deeply%20influenced%20by%20its%20ideology.%20It%20has%20cloned%20its%20ideology%20in%20Hezbollah%20in%20Lebanon%20and%20the%20Houthis%20in%20Yemen.%20Its%20ideological%20fingerprints%20are%20all%20over%20Syria%20and%20Iraq%20too.%20Additionally%2C%20Tehran's%20influence%20is%20creeping%20into%20parts%20of%20the%20Gulf%2C%20with%20Bahrain%2C%20a%20Shia-majority%20country%2C%20being%20a%20notable%20example.%20It's%20also%20trying%20to%20make%20inroads%20into%20Afghanistan%20and%20even%20in%20places%20like%20the%20Palestinian%20territories.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20if%20you%20are%20looking%20for%20where%20else%20Iran's%20revolution%20is%20spreading%20much%20beyond%20its%20boundaries%2C%20just%20visit%20the%20Shia%20majority%20Kargil%20in%20Kashmir.%20The%20life-size%20cutout%20of%20Khamenei%20outside%20a%20Shia%20mosque%20in%20the%20main%20town%20says%20it%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%202009%2C%20right%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20US%20and%20UN%20sanctions%2C%20Iran%20had%20completed%20around%20several%20hundred%20development%20projects%20in%20southern%20Lebanon%20-%20schools%2C%20religious%20centres%2C%20sports%20complexes%2C%20hospitals%20-you%20name%20it.%20And%20all%20of%20them%20conveniently%20spread%20Tehran's%20Islamic%20ideology.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20question%20is%2C%20why%20does%20Iran%20support%20Hamas%20and%2C%20more%20generally%2C%20all%20Palestinians%2C%20even%20though%20they%20are%20Sunni%20who%20have%20not%20accepted%20its%20Shia%20revolution%3F%20The%20answer%20is%20simple.%20The%20clerical%20regime%20asserts%20it%20is%20its%20Islamic%20duty%20to%20be%20the%20defender%20of%20what%20it%20believes%20is%20the%20oppressed%20people.%20To%20support%20the%20oppressed%20and%20oppose%20the%20oppressor%20is%20at%20the%20core%20of%20the%20Shia%20doctrine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EShiite%20Doctrine%20Of%20Sacrifice%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20the%20early%20years%20of%20Islam%2C%20the%20followers%20were%20divided%20into%20Sunni%20and%20Shia%20sects.%20The%20former%20enjoys%20the%20majority%20and%20the%20latter's%20population%20is%20restricted%20to%20West%20Asia%2C%20Pakistan%20and%20India.%20Persia%20had%20a%20vibrant%20ancient%20culture.%20After%20embracing%20Shia%20Islam%2C%20the%20Persian%20pride%20in%20culture%20remains%20strong%20in%20Iran.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUrdu%20poet%20Allama%20Iqbal%20has%20summed%20up%20the%20spirit%20of%20Shiite%20martyrdom%20in%20this%20couplet%3A%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3EIslam%20zinda%20hota%20hai%20har%20karbala%20ke%20baad%3C%2Fem%3E%26quot%3B%20(Islam%20is%20revived%20after%20every%20Karbala-like%20tragedy).%20The%20Shiite%20spirit%20of%20martyrdom%20is%20deeply%20rooted%20in%20the%20tragedy%20of%20Karbala%2C%20where%20Imam%20Hussain%2C%20the%20grandson%20of%20Prophet%20Muhammad%2C%20and%20his%20followers%2C%20were%20brutally%20killed%20in%20their%20stand%20against%20tyranny.%20This%20sacrifice%20is%20seen%20not%20just%20as%20a%20historical%20event%20but%20as%20a%20timeless%20symbol%20of%20resistance%2C%20justice%2C%20and%20self-sacrifice%20for%20a%20higher%20cause.%20In%20Shiite%20belief%2C%20martyrdom%20is%20the%20ultimate%20act%20of%20devotion%20and%20defiance%20against%20oppression%2C%20which%20has%20been%20encapsulated%20in%20the%20Islamic%20Republic%20of%20Iran's%20ideology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETherefore%2C%20US%20sanctions%20or%20Israeli%20attacks%20on%20its%20infrastructure%20only%20hardens%20a%20Shiite's%20resolve%20to%20resist%20and%20defy.%20Take%2C%20for%20example%2C%20how%20over%20the%20last%20four%20years%2C%20the%20Israeli%20campaign%20against%20Iran%2C%20which%20has%20seen%20sabotage%20and%20attacks%20on%20nuclear%20and%20military%20facilities%20within%20Iran%2C%20assassinations%20of%20nuclear%20scientists%20and%20decorated%20military%20officers%20on%20Iranian%20soil%20and%20even%20elsewhere%20in%20Syria%2C%20Lebanon%2C%20Yemen%20and%20other%20locations%2C%20have%20failed%20to%20deter%20Iran%20or%20Hezbollah%20from%20harming%20the%20Israeli%20cause.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20may%20launch%20an%20attack%20on%20Iran%20and%20destroy%20its%20oil%20fields%20or%20other%20infrastructure%20in%20retaliation%20to%20the%20October%201%20attack%2C%20but%20it%20is%20quite%20possible%20it%20will%20only%20firm%20up%20the%20Shiite%20resolve%20to%20launch%20further%20attacks%20on%20Israel.%20It%20might%20become%20a%20never-ending%20cycle%20of%20violence%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Competition%20To%20Win%20Over%20Muslims%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuch%20before%20the%20Islamic%20Republic%20of%20Iran%20began%20exporting%20its%20ideology%2C%20it%20was%20Saudi%20Arabia%20that%20was%20engaged%20in%20winning%20the%20hearts%20and%20minds%20of%20the%20Muslim%20world.%20The%20export%20of%20Wahhabism%20gained%20momentum%20during%20King%20Faisal's%20reign%20(1964-1975)%20and%20continued%20under%20subsequent%20monarchs.%20Its%20primary%20objective%20was%20to%20promote%20Wahhabism%2C%20support%20Muslim%20communities%20worldwide%20and%20counter%20Shia%20and%20Iranian%20influence.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Wahhabi%20Mission%20and%20Saudi%20Arabia%26quot%3B%20by%20David%20Commins%20encapsulates%20the%20rise%20of%20Wahhabi%20ideology%20quite%20well.%20Wahhabism%20took%20an%20extreme%20form%20in%20some%20societies%2C%20which%20gave%20birth%20to%20entities%20such%20as%20the%20Taliban%20and%20Al%20Qaeda.%20There%20was%20no%20surprise%20in%20the%20fact%20that%20out%20of%20the%2019%20hijackers%20of%20planes%20in%20the%209%2F11%20terror%20attack%2C%2015%20were%20Saudi%20nationals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20ironic%20then%20that%20the%20US%20would%20continue%20to%20nurture%20monarchs%20in%20Saudi%20Arabia.%20Of%20course%2C%20there%20is%20no%20denying%20that%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20Saudi%20Arabia%20has%20attempted%20to%20rebrand%20itself%20as%20a%20force%20against%20extremism%2C%20introducing%20reforms%20under%20Crown%20Prince%20Mohammed%20bin%20Salman's%20'Vision%202030'.%20However%2C%20critics%20argue%20that%20these%20reforms%20are%20superficial%20and%20the%20underlying%20Wahhabi%20ideology%20remains%20intact.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ESaudi%20Influence%20Wanes%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaudi%20Arabia%20was%20on%20the%20brink%20of%20signing%20the%20Abraham%20Accord%20with%20Israel%20before%20the%20deadly%20attack%20by%20Hamas%20on%20October%207%20last%20year.%20Many%20in%20Muslim%20societies%20complain%20that%20Saudis%20appear%20to%20be%20doing%20nothing%20for%20the%20Palestinians%20in%20Gaza%20and%20the%20West%20Bank.%20On%20the%20contrary%2C%20it%20is%20being%20accused%20of%20cold-shouldering%20the%20Palestinian%20issue.%20Clearly%2C%20with%20Iran%20positioned%20to%20take%20on%20powerful%20forces%20like%20Israel%20and%20America%2C%20Saudi%20Arabia%20is%20losing%20the%20battle%20of%20winning%20the%20hearts%20and%20minds%20of%20Muslims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20West%20Asia%20is%20a%20complex%20region.%20Arabs%2C%20Turks%20and%20Persians%20are%20the%20largest%20ethnic%20or%20linguistic%20groups%20there.%20Together%2C%20they%20make%20up%2090%25%20of%20the%20region's%20population.%20The%20Arab%20population%20is%20divided%20into%20over%2020%20countries.%20Turks%20and%20Iranians%20largely%20live%20in%20Turkey%20and%20Iran%2C%20respectively.%20Much%20of%20the%20current%20Arab%20countries%20and%20the%20land%20where%20Israel%20stands%20today%20were%20until%20the%20First%20World%20War%20part%20of%20the%20Ottoman%20Empire.%20So%2C%20Turkish%20influence%20in%20the%20region%20cannot%20be%20ignored.%20Turkey%20Muslims%20practise%20Sunni%20Islam%20but%20they%20are%20more%20moderate%20compared%20to%20the%20Saudi%20brand%20of%20Islam.%20Modern%20Turkey%2C%20under%20President%20Erdogan%2C%20is%20engaged%20in%20spreading%20its%20cultural%20and%20political%20influences%20across%20the%20Muslim%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EIran%20Is%20Far%20From%20Isolated%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20widely%20believed%20that%20due%20to%20sanctions%20imposed%20by%20the%20US%20since%201979%2C%20the%20Islamic%20Republic%20of%20Iran%20stands%20isolated.%20The%20sanctions%20have%20no%20doubt%20hugely%20impacted%20its%20economy%2C%20but%20the%20country%20has%20still%20managed%20to%20create%20a%20huge%20missile%20production%20industry%20and%20manufacture%20the%20most%20modern%20drones.%20Iran%20has%20not%20only%20built%20its%20axis%20of%20resistance%20in%20Hezbollah%20and%20the%20Houthis%2C%20but%20it%20has%20also%20nurtured%20good%20diplomatic%20ties%20with%20key%20regional%20players%2C%20such%20as%20Turkey%2C%20Iraq%2C%20Syria%2C%20Qatar%20and%2C%20more%20recently%2C%20even%20with%20Saudi%20Arabia.%20In%20the%20last%20two%20years%2C%20it%20has%20become%20part%20of%20geopolitically%20important%20multilateral%20fora%2C%20such%20as%20BRICS%20and%20the%20Shanghai%20Cooperation%20Organisation%20(SCO).%20A%20strong%20anti-US%20sentiment%20has%20also%20brought%20Iran%20and%20Russia%20much%20closer%20together%2C%20which%20is%20indeed%20a%20big%20deal%20for%20the%20former.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20once%20had%20an%20excellent%20relationship%20with%20Iran%20after%20it%20helped%20depose%20an%20elected%20Prime%20Minister%20and%20install%20a%20monarch%20in%201953.%20It%20continued%20to%20support%20the%20oppressive%20regime%20of%20the%20Pahlavi%20monarchy%20until%20the%201979%20Islamic%20revolution%20replaced%20the%20tyrant%20administration.%20In%20a%20way%2C%20the%20US%20is%20indirectly%20responsible%20for%20the%20Islamic%20revolution%20and%20for%20oppressed%20Iranians%20under%20the%20monarchy%20finding%20refuge%20in%20the%20Shiite%20faith.%20True%20to%20its%20habit%2C%20the%20US%20has%20often%20supported%20dictators%20and%20anti-democracy%20leaders%20in%20West%20Asia.%20Military%20dictatorships%20in%20Egypt%20and%20the%20monarchies%20in%20Saudi%20Arabia%20and%20Jordan%20continue%20to%20depend%20on%20the%20US%20security%20umbrella.%20Maybe%20there%20is%20a%20need%20for%20a%20West%20Asia%20policy%20reset.%20But%20then%20there%20are%20hawks%20in%20the%20US%20Congress%20and%20inside%20Israel%20for%20whom%20any%20rapprochement%20with%20Iran%20will%20be%20tantamount%20to%20blasphemy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Syed%20Zubair%20Ahmed%20is%20a%20London-based%20senior%20Indian%20journalist%20with%20three%20decades%20of%20experience%20with%20the%20Western%20media)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729235280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2F8s66n2ug_iran_625x300_11_October_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Firan-is-under-fire-but-its-still-winning-the-ideological-war-6816583%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22What%20Iran%20cannot%20do%20militarily%20to%20Israel%2C%20it's%20doing%20with%20its%20soft%20power.%20It%20has%20encircled%20the%20Jewish%20state%20with%20a%20web%20of%20entities%20deeply%20influenced%20by%20its%20ideology.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Firan-is-under-fire-but-its-still-winning-the-ideological-war-6816583%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Newfoundland%20residents%20discover%20strange%20'white%20blobs'%20washing%20up%20on%20beaches%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729235206000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-114341714%2Cimgsize-2233871.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fnewfoundland-residents-discover-strange-white-blobs-washing-up-on-beaches%2Farticleshow%2F114340440.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F114340440.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EResidents%20of%20Newfoundland%20have%20discovered%20peculiar%20white%20blobs%20washing%20ashore%20along%20Placentia%20Bay.%20Locals%20describe%20them%20as%20doughy%20with%20a%20vegetable%20oil%20smell.%20Init