E%5CnHe%20was%20killed%20in%20Rafah%20by%20the%20brave%20soldiers%20of%20the%20Israel%20Defense%20Forces.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnWhile%20this%20is%20not%20the%20end%20of%20the%20war%20in%20Gaza%2C%20it's%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20end.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FC6wAaLH1YW%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FC6wAaLH1YW%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20-%20%D7%91%D7%A0%D7%99%D7%9E%D7%99%D7%9F%20%D7%A0%D7%AA%D7%A0%D7%99%D7%94%D7%95%20(%40netanyahu)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnetanyahu%2Fstatus%2F1847026551629795532%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EOctober%2017%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Israel%20Defence%20Forces%20revealed%20on%20Thursday%20that%20Sinwar%2C%20along%20with%20two%20other%20terrorists%20have%20been%20eliminated%20by%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdrone-footage-of-hamas-chief-yahya-sinwars-last-moments-released-by-israel-6815660%5C%22%3EDrone%20Footage%20Of%20Hamas%20Chief%20Yahya%20Sinwar's%20Last%20Moments%20Released%20By%20Israel%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENetanyahu%20revealed%20that%20Hamas%20is%20currently%20holding%20101%20hostages%20in%20Gaza%2C%20comprising%20citizens%20from%2023%20different%20countries%2C%20including%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHamas%20is%20holding%20101%20hostages%20in%20Gaza%20who%20are%20citizens%20of%2023%20countries%2C%20citizens%20of%20Israel%2C%20but%20citizens%20of%20many%20other%20countries.%20Israel%20is%20committed%20to%20doing%20everything%20in%20our%20power%20to%20bring%20all%20of%20them%20home.%20Israel%20will%20guarantee%20the%20safety%20of%20all%20those%20who%20return%20our%20hostages%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20PM%20issued%20a%20stern%20warning%20to%20those%20holding%20Israeli%20hostages%2C%20vowing%20that%20Israel%20will%20relentlessly%20pursue%20and%20bring%20them%20to%20justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20to%20those%20who%20would%20harm%20our%20hostages%2C%20I%20have%20another%20message%20-%20Israel%20will%20hunt%20you%20down%20and%20bring%20you%20to%20justice.%20But%20to%20those%20who%20would%20harm%20our%20hostages%2C%20I%20have%20another%20message%20-%20Israel%20will%20hunt%20you%20down%20and%20bring%20you%20to%20justice.%20I%20also%20have%20a%20message%20of%20hope%20to%20the%20people%20of%20the%20region%20-%20the%20axis%20of%20terror%20that%20was%20built%20by%20Iran%20is%20collapsing%20before%20our%20eyes%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhezbollah-to-escalate-war-with-israel-after-hamas-leader-yahya-sinwar-killed-6815260%5C%22%3EHezbollah%20To%20Escalate%20War%20With%20Israel%20After%20Hamas%20Leader%20Yahya%20Sinwar%20Killed%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENetanyahu%20in%20his%20message%20also%20highlighted%20the%20elimination%20of%20key%20Hezbollah%20leaders%2C%20including%20Hassan%20Nasrallah%2C%20and%20asserted%20that%20the%20reign%20of%20terror%20imposed%20by%20the%20Iranian%20regime%20on%20its%20own%20people%20and%20those%20in%20Iraq%2C%20Syria%2C%20Lebanon%2C%20and%20Yemen%20will%20%26quot%3Bcome%20to%20an%20end.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNasrallah%20is%20gone%2C%20his%20deputy%20Mohsen%20is%20gone%2C%20Haniyeh%20is%20gone%2C%20Deif%20is%20gone%2C%20Sinwar%20is%20gone.%20The%20reign%20of%20terror%20that%20the%20Iranian%20regime%20has%20imposed%20on%20its%20own%20people%20and%20on%20the%20peoples%20of%20Iraq%2C%20Syria%2C%20Lebanon%20and%20Yemen%2C%20too%20will%20come%20to%20an%20end%2C%26quot%3B%20Netanyahu%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BAll%20those%20who%20seek%20a%20future%20of%20prosperity%20and%20peace%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20should%20unite%20to%20build%20a%20better%20future.%20Together%2C%20we%20can%20push%20back%20the%20forces%20of%2