rvices.%20Armed%20with%20a%20degree%20in%20electrical%20engineering%20from%20NIT%20Kurukshetra%2C%20he%20set%20his%20sights%20on%20UPSC%20preparation%20after%20graduating%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComing%20from%20a%20rural%20background%2C%20Karamveer%20was%20deeply%20affected%20by%20the%20disconnect%20he%20observed%20between%20government%20officials%20and%20the%20common%20public%20in%20his%20hometown.%20This%20ignited%20his%20desire%20to%20bridge%20the%20gap%20and%20work%20towards%20creating%20a%20more%20harmonious%20relationship%20between%20authorities%20and%20the%20people%20they%20served.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInitially%20aspiring%20to%20join%20the%20Army%2C%20he%20faced%20challenges%20during%20his%20attempts%2C%20eventually%20pivoting%20towards%20the%20UPSC%20path.%20But%20his%20journey%20towards%20UPSC%20success%20was%20fraught%20with%20setbacks%2C%20particularly%20regarding%20the%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2Fweb-stories%2Fias-ips-officers-share-useful-tips-to-prepare-for-csat-qualifying-paper-of-the-upsc-exam%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Civil%20Services%20Aptitude%20Test%20%3C%2Fa%3E(CSAT)%20component.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20the%20UPSC%20Civil%20Services%20Exam%20(preliminary)%2C%20the%20CSAT%20tests%20the%20analytical%20skills%2C%20reasoning%20ability%2C%20and%20aptitude%20of%20aspirants.%20Candidates%20need%20to%20score%20only%2033%20percent%2C%20as%20this%20paper%20is%20qualifying%20in%20nature.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKaramveer%20excelled%20in%20the%20General%20Studies%20paper%20of%20the%20prelims%2C%20but%20the%20CSAT%20exam%20proved%20to%20be%20a%20significant%20hurdle%20in%20his%20initial%20attempts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20familial%20pressures%2C%20uncertainties%2C%20and%20previous%20setbacks%2C%20Karamveer%20remained%20steadfast%20in%20his%20determination.%20His%20perseverance%20and%20dedicated%20preparation%20eventually%20paid%20off%20in%20his%20thi