4%2F10%2Fhealthcare-access-in-tribal-areas-3-1728467967.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dr%20Rani%20Bhang%20is%20an%20MD%20in%20obstetrics%20and%20gynaecology%20and%20specialises%20in%20women's%20health%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fhealthcare-access-in-tribal-areas-3-1728467967.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fhealthcare-access-in-tribal-areas-3-1728467967-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fhealthcare-access-in-tribal-areas-3-1728467967-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fhealthcare-access-in-tribal-areas-3-1728467967-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fhealthcare-access-in-tribal-areas-3-1728467967-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-369365%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDr%20Rani%20Bang%20is%20an%20MD%20in%20obstetrics%20and%20gynaecology%20and%20specialises%20in%20women%E2%80%99s%20health.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20their%20opinion%2C%20scanty%20or%20normal%20menstruation%20indicates%20that%20the%20blood%20is%20collecting%20in%20the%20uterus%2C%20forming%20lumps%2C%20and%20will%20eventually%20impinge%20on%20their%20vital%20organs%20and%20cause%20death.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20lack%20of%20proper%20diagnoses%20extends%20to%20children%E2%80%99s%20healthcare%20as%20well%2C%20she%20figured.%20%E2%80%9CInitially%2C%20when%20we%20started%20working%20in%20Gadchiroli%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F116337%2Fgood-news-india-averted-million-child-deaths-since-2005%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einfant%20mortality%3C%2Fa%3E%20rate%20was%20121%20per%201%2C000%20(indicating%20