20shift%20in%20infrastructure%20(both%20public%20and%20digital)%20motivated%20us%20to%20look%20for%20a%20business%20model%20that%20would%20take%20care%20of%20the%20realities%20of%20these%20%5Brural%5D%20markets.%20We%20intended%20to%20target%20underbanked%20but%20creditworthy%20homes%2C%E2%80%9D%20Utpal%20notes.%20Together%20with%20Sameer%20Mishra%2C%20who%20has%20over%2020%20years%20of%20experience%20in%20rural%20finance%2C%20he%20founded%20SarvaGram%20%E2%80%94%20which%20has%20changed%20many%20lives%20like%20Ishwargowda%E2%80%99s%20with%20access%20to%20credit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20%5BSarvaGram%5D%20isn%E2%80%99t%20an%20overnight%20dream%2C%20but%20instead%2C%20a%20continuing%20success%20story%2C%E2%80%9D%20Utpal%20points%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EGiving%20rural%20households%20agency%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20Ishwargowda%E2%80%99s%20creditworthiness%20were%20to%20be%20assessed%20solely%20based%20on%20his%20income%20at%20the%20time%2C%20or%20his%20discretionary%20expenses%2C%20he%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20have%20made%20the%20cut.%20A%20lack%20of%20steady%20income%20was%20why%20he%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20considered%20for%20a%20formal%20bank%20loan.%20To%20this%20end%2C%20when%20Utpal%20set%20out%20to%20conceive%20SarvaGram%2C%20he%20was%20keen%20to%20build%20it%20with%20a%20growth-oriented%20ethos%20that%20would%20provide%20loans%20to%20those%20with%20variable%20incomes%2C%20but%20aspirational%20mindsets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20as%20%E2%80%9CIndia%E2%80%99s%20first%20household-centric%2C%20data-led%2C%20%E2%80%98high-tech%20high-touch%E2%80%99%20distribution%20platform%E2%80%9D%2C%20SarvaGram%20is%20extending%20a%20hand%20towards%20rural%20India%20through%20its%20bouquet%20of%20financial%20and%20productivity-enhancing%20offerings.%20The%20cornerstone%20of%20the%20organisation%E2%80%99s%20services%20has%20been%20a%20keen%20focus%20on%20the%20%E2%80%9Cunderbanked%20but%20creditworthy%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FUyhbciwOdQ8%3Fsi%3DJKgdl5rOGHAG-GMb%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPutting%20this%20into%20perspective%2C%20Utpal%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20decided%20to%20focus%20on%20mid-income%20households%20that%20may%20not%20necessarily%20have%20banking%20records%20or%20credit%20track%20records%20to%20prove%20their%20creditworthiness.%20Instead%2C%20their%20creditworthiness%20is%20determined%20by%20their%20%E2%80%98intent%20to%20repay%E2%80%99.%20These%20are%20not%20data-dark%20households%20anymore.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20impact%20ripples%20of%20SarvaGram%20are%20currently%20reaching%20over%2016%2C000%20villages%20across%20India%2C%20making%20it%20the%20gold%20standard%20in%20how%20tech%20can%20be%20leveraged%20to%20scale%20the%20dreams%20of%20households%20that%20once%20did%20not%20come%20under%20the%20purview%20of%20formal%20banking.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Ishwargowda%20is%20reaping%20the%20benefits%20of%20his%20association%20with%20SarvaGram%20at%20his%20%3Cem%3Ekirana%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Ea%20few%20kilometres%20away%2C%20farmer%20Hanumanthappa%20Lingappa%E2%80%99s%20fate%20mirrors%20the%20same%20success.%20It%20will%20be%20a%20decade%20now%20since%20the%20farmer%20has%20been%20cultivating%20sugarcane.%20The%20land%20is%20cropping%20well%20%E2%80%94%20as%20suggested%20by%20the%20sweet%20drink%20that%20the%20farmer%20offers%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fenterpreneurship-in-rural-india-1-1727933757.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Farmer%20Hanumanthappa%20Lingappa%20cultivates%20sugarcane%20while%20also%20collecting%20grains%20from%20neighbouring%20farmers%20and%20selling%20it%20to%20the%20Farmer%20Producer%20Organisations%20(FPOs)%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fenterpreneurship-in-rural-india-1-1727933757.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fenterpreneurship-in-rural-india-1-1727933757-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fenterpreneurship-in-rural-india-1-1727933757-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fenterpreneurship-in-rural-india-1-1727933757-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fenterpreneurship-in-rural-india-1-1727933757-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-368491%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EFarmer%20Hanumanthappa%20Lingappa%20cultivates%20sugarcane%20while%20also%20collecting%20grains%20from%20neighbouring%20farmers%20and%20selling%20them%20to%20the%20Farmer%20Producer%20Organisations%20(FPOs)%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20quick%20tour%20through%20Hanumanthappa%E2%80%99s%20home%20and%20the%20fields%20that%20extend%20for%20miles%20beyond%20the%20backdoor%20is%20a%20nod%20to%20his%20thriving%20business(es)%3B%20note%20the%20use%20of%20plural!%20You%20see%2C%20Hanumanthappa%20is%20championing%20two%20endeavours%2C%20simultaneously.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20he%20explains%2C%20sugarcane%20farming%2C%20though%20lucrative%2C%20isn%E2%80%99t%20dependable%20%E2%80%94%20fluctuating%20seasons%20and%20variable%20soil%20patterns%20play%20spoilsport%C2%A0%20%E2%80%94%20and%20so%20he%20conceived%20another%20business%20which%20entails%20him%20collecting%20grains%20from%20the%20neighbouring%20farmers%20and%20selling%20them%20to%20a%20Farmer%20Producer%20Organisation%20(FPO).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%2057-year-old%20applied%20for%20a%20loan%20through%20SarvaGram%20for%20the%20same%2C%20he%20was%20prepared%20to%20wait.%20He%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20a%20stranger%20to%20the%20harrowing%20experiences%20that%20farmers%20had%20to%20endure%20to%20get%20access%20to%20credit.%20So%2C%20you%20can%20imagine%20his%20surprise%20when%20in%2020%20days%2C%20the%20loan%20was%20disbursed%20and%20his%20business%20was%20ready%20to%20take%20off.%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99ve%20told%20many%20others%20to%20take%20advantage%20of%20the%20scheme%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20beams%2C%20adding%20that%20so%20far%2C%20his%20earnings%20have%20increased%20by%20Rs%2010%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHinged%20on%20social%20and%20trade%20capital%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20farmers%20like%20Hanumanthappa%2C%20FPOs%20are%20akin%20to%20catalysts%20that%20make%20revolutions%20possible.%20Anil%20Kumar%20SG%2C%20founder%20and%20CEO%20of%20Samunnati%2C%20agrees.%20Years%20ago%2C%20Anil%20and%20Pravesh%20Sharma%20IAS%20(retired)%2C%20Director%20of%20Samunnati%20Agro%20spotted%20an%20opportunity%20in%20this%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Pravesh%20%E2%80%94%20also%20known%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98Godfather%20of%20the%20FPO%E2%80%99%20anchored%20and%20championed%20FPOs%20in%20Small%20Farmers%E2%80%99%20Agri-business%20Consortium%2C%20Anil%20pioneered%20the%20financing%20model%20of%20Samunnati%2C%20which%20today%20works%20with%20thousands%20of%20FPOs.%20The%20duo%E2%80%99s%20passion%20for%20seeing%20India%E2%80%99s%20rural%20hinterland%20scale%20its%20operations%20translated%20into%20Samunnati%E2%80%99s%20mission.%20Today%2C%20the%20organisation%20has%20access%20to%20over%206%2C500%20FPOs%20and%20is%20approaching%20the%2010%2C000%20FPO%20mark.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fenterpreneurship-in-rural-india-2-1727933914.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Pravesh%20Sharma%20IAS%20(retired)%20and%20Anil%20Kumar%20SG%20have%20pioneered%20Samunnati%20which%20works%20with%20thousands%20of%20FPOs%20across%20India%20to%20provide%20farmers%20with%20market%20linkages%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fenterpreneurship-in-rural-india-2-1727933914.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fenterpreneurship-in-rural-india-2-1727933914-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fenterpreneurship-in-rural-india-2-1727933914-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fenterpreneurship-in-rural-india-2-1727933914-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fenterpreneurship-in-rural-india-2-1727933914-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-368493%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EPravesh%20Sharma%20IAS%20(retired)%20and%20Anil%20Kumar%20SG%20have%20pioneered%20Samunnati%20which%20works%20with%20thousands%20of%20FPOs%20across%20India%20to%20provide%20farmers%20with%20market%20linkages%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20drive%20through%20Hubbali%E2%80%99s%20beautiful%20landscapes%20makes%20one%20privy%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3Emandis%20%3C%2Fem%3E(markets)%20and%20beautiful%20village%20homes%2C%20there%20are%20very%20few%20banks%20in%20sight.%20Pravesh%20explains%20the%20reason%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20parlance%20of%20the%20financial%20world%2C%20banks%20have%20not%20seen%20this%20sector%20as%20an%20attractive%20asset%20class.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20where%20Samunnati%20enters.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20organisation%E2%80%99s%20genius%20has%20been%20to%20show%20that%20this%20asset%20class%20can%20be%20a%20rewarding%20one%2C%20provided%20it%20is%20structured%20correctly%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pravesh%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20Samunnati%2C%20the%20focus%20is%20on%20smallholder%20farmers%20as%20the%20main%20beneficiaries%3B%20a%20paradigm%20shift%20in%20the%20existing%20economic%20view%20and%20opinions.%20But%20it%20was%20vital%20that%20the%20organisation%20be%20designed%20on%20this%20crux%20for%20Anil%2C%20whose%20two-decade-long%20association%20with%20the%20banking%20sector%20introduced%20him%20to%20the%20woes%20of%20agri-enterprises%20that%20lacked%20access%20to%20credit%20and%20loans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20providing%20smallholder%20farmers%20and%20agri%20enterprises%20access%20to%20markets%2C%20financial%20intermediation%2C%20market%20linkages%20and%20advisory%20services%2C%20Samunnati%20enables%20them%20to%20operate%20at%20a%20higher%20equilibrium.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EIt%20is%20a%20standing%20example%20of%20how%20entrepreneurship%20can%20be%20targeted%20at%20providing%20commercially%20viable%20solutions%20to%20a%20customer%20segment%2C%20which%20is%20often%20misunderstood%2C%20and%20sidelined.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20operational%20results%20are%20a%20nod%20to%20their%20incredible%20work%2C%20Anil%20maintains%20that%20the%20organisation%20has%20a%20larger%20goal%20%E2%80%94%20to%20set%20an%20example.%20%E2%80%9CThrough%20Samunnati%2C%20we%20have%20established%20that%20lending%20to%20farmers%20is%20credible%2C%20sustainable%20and%20scalable.%20Samunnati%20has%20demonstrated%20the%20scalability%20of%20lending%20to%20agriculture%2C%20and%20this%20will%20foster%20a%20lot%20of%20banks%20coming%20into%20the%20sector.%20As%20I%20see%20it%2C%20the%20flow%20of%20credit%20to%20the%20agricultural%20sector%20is%20poised%20to%20take%20a%20big%20leap.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFarmer%20Mrutunjay%20Shankar%20Salimate%2C%20leader%20of%20Kalmeshwara%20FPO%2C%20which%20has%20benefitted%20from%20its%20association%20with%20Samunnati%2C%20reminisces%20how%20in%202016%20when%20they%20started%2C%20they%20were%20just%20a%20group%20of%2050%20farmers.%20%E2%80%9CNow%20we%20have%20more%20than%201%2C400%20farmers%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20The%20association%20with%20Samunnati%20has%20been%20a%20shot%20in%20the%20arm%20for%20the%20FPO%E2%80%99s%20work%20of%20supporting%20farmers%20with%20seeds%2C%20fertilisers%2C%20spray%20pumps%2C%20supply%20chain%20operations%2C%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FAvbGO0-Rux8%3Fsi%3DaYFKg-1D4pcxdTAq%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMrutunjay%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CThey%20have%20provided%20us%20with%20market%20linkages%2C%20networking%20with%20institutions%20and%20financial%20support.%20They%20have%20also%20conducted%20activities%20to%20identify%20village-level%20entrepreneurs.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESarvaGram%20and%20Samunnati%E2%80%99s%20success%20stories%20are%20reflective%20of%20how%20entrepreneurs%20can%20create%20businesses%20that%20address%20the%20growing%20aspirations%20of%20millions%20of%20Entrepreneurial%20Households%3Csup%3ETM%3C%2Fsup%3E%20across%20India%2C%20to%20address%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.enmasse.world%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEPIC%20Opportunity%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20EPIC%20Opportunity%20is%20a%20description%20of%20the%20multi-trillion%20dollar%20market%20opportunity%20that%20Entrepreneurial%20Households%20represent.%20For%20investors%2C%20it%20provides%20an%20opportunity%20to%20deploy%20capital%20for%20the%20creation%20of%20large%2C%20formal%20institutions%20addressing%20the%20demands%20of%20Entrepreneurial%20Households%2C%20across%20emerging%20markets.%20This%20burgeoning%20asset%20class%20is%20fast%20proving%20to%20be%20the%20new%20centre%20of%20gravity%20of%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20and%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20economic%20prosperity.%20By%20tapping%20into%20the%20potential%20of%20these%20households%2C%20companies%20like%20SarvaGram%20and%20Samunnati%20are%20leading%20the%20way%20and%20showcasing%20that%20impact%20and%20commercial%20returns%20can%20go%20hand-in-hand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20growth%20story%20is%20set%20to%20take%20on%20a%20new%20narrative.%20Proof%20of%20this%20lies%20in%20my%20conversation%20with%20farmer%20Mrutunjay.%20While%20a%20wide%20array%20of%20opportunities%20are%20open%20to%20his%20children%2C%20he%20says%2C%20they%20are%20keen%20on%20following%20in%20his%20footsteps.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20want%20to%20grow%20up%20to%20be%20farmers.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ELeading%20change%20from%20the%20front%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20landscape%20in%20remote%20areas%20of%20India%20does%20seem%20promising.%20And%20the%20feeling%20continues%20402%20km%20away%2C%20in%20Bengaluru.%20Dreams%20are%20brimming%20at%20the%20Nisarga%20Vidyanikethana%20High%20School%2C%20as%20hundreds%20of%20kids%20who%20study%20at%20the%20school%20share%20their%20aspirations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20want%20to%20get%20into%20sports%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20a%2010-year-old.%20While%20another%20says%20he%20will%20join%20the%20Army.%20Hearing%20these%20innocent%20dreams%20has%20school%20head%20Nandan%20Eshwar%20beaming.%20Since%20its%20inception%2C%20the%20school%20has%20served%20as%20a%20space%20for%20budding%20talent.%20Nandan%2C%20whose%20uncle%20Channakeshava%20built%20the%20school%2C%20has%20always%20admired%20the%20students%E2%80%99%20persistence%20to%20learn%20and%20dream%20big.%20His%20uncle%2C%20he%20says%2C%20would%20be%20thrilled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C